P: I haven't seen any blood.

D: OK, do you feel wheezy at all?

P: I haven't noticed any wheezing. 

D: OK, how about shortness of breath?

P: Usually well, after some of my coughing fits, I can be a little bit shorter in breath, but otherwise they've been. 

