D: OK. Do these headaches feel like the same headaches?

P: Yeah, they they feel about the same, kind of like a pressure or vice grip on my head.

D: OK, so it's not like the worst headache you've ever experienced?

P: No, I think it's just been a part of how I haven't been feeling well these these last few days.

D: OK, yeah. Do you feel fatigued or tired at all?

P: Yeah, for sure. I haven't really had any changes, but just haven't been really getting my work done throughout the day because I have just been feeling so tired.

D: Yeah, umm, and do you feel any sort of body aches that go along with your fatigue?

P: Maybe a little. 

D: OK. Umm, can you think of anything that may have caused your symptoms? You know, have you been in contact with anyone who's been sick recently? 

